Customizeable, upgradeable, is GPS capable, etc.  A must-download if you ever travel and want a reasonably sized off-line map program on your desktop computer (Laptop especially).

After installation, i had to goto the 
c:\program files x86\ microsoft streets and trips 2010 then right click on 'Streets.exe', then 'Send to Desktop'
Then, I had to right click on the desktop icon, then goto properties, then to Compatibility, then put a check mark in the box 'Run as Administrator'.

Runs fine and dandy now. VL though.
